"  priority [prio] [from [src]] [to [dst]], ,...\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Ange en lista över IPv6-routingregler formaterade som:\n"
"  priority [prio] [from [src]] [to [dst]], ,...\n"
"\n"

